name: Pacsafe Wrapsafe Adjustable Cable Lock
description: Secure your bags at packed airports, or lock down luggage on your roof rack. This lightweight but heavy-duty cable lock wraps tight so it can’t be easily clipped off.Cable is made of polycarbonate and high-tensile stainless steel wire.Includes combination lock.Cable length is 2.5m.Wraps any item with a circumference of 70–170cm.Comes with a storage pouch for travel.
